description: Gorgeous, sun-filled 2-bed, 2-bath penthouse condo in City Point. Open-concept living & kitchen area boasts soaring vaulted ceilings, multiple skylights & exposed brick accents. Modern kitchen features white cabinetry, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances + an island w/ a breakfast bar. The primary suite features a spacious double-door closet & a beautiful paneled accent wall, complete w/ an en suite bath w/ marble tile & radiant heated floor. A generous, queen-sized second bedroom w/ a double-door closet & beautiful exposed brick. Brazilian Cherry hardwood floors throughout, in-unit washer/dryer, built-in speakers & a large private back deck + exclusive roof rights. Located on one of South Boston’s most picturesque tree-lined streets, this brick building is directly across from the beautiful Lincoln Square Garden. Plus, just a few blocks from East Broadway restaurants, the beach & bridge to Seaport. Don’t miss your chance to own this one-of-a-kind, centrally located gem!
